\c 31
\s Dhavhidhi anokumbira kubatsirwa, achivonga unyoro hwaJehovha
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Jehovha, ndinovimba nemi; ngandirege kutongonyadziswa; Ndirwirei pakururama kwenyu.
\v 2 Rerekerai nzeve yenyu kwandiri; kurumidzai kundirwira; Ivai dombo rangu rakasimba, neimba yenhare yokundiponesa.
\v 3 Nokuti ndimi dombo rangu nenhare yangu; Naizvozvo nditungamirirei mundifambise nokuda kwezita renyu.
\v 4 Ndibvutei pamumbure wavakandidzikira pakavanda; Nokuti ndimi nhare yangu.
\v 5 Ndinoisa mweya wangu muruoko rwenyu; Makandidzikunura Jehovha, imi Mwari wazvokwadi.
\v 6 Ndinovenga vanokudza zvenhema zvisina maturo; Asi ndichavimba naJehovha.
\v 7 Ndichafara nokufarisisa netsitsi dzenyu; Nokuti makaona kutambudzika kwangu; Makaziva kumanikidzwa kwomweya wangu;
\v 8 Hamuna kundiisa muruoko rwomuvengi; Makamisa tsoka dzangu panzvimbo yakafarikana.
\v 9 Ndinzwirei tsitsi Jehovha, nokuti ndiri panjodzi; Ziso rangu rapera nokuchema, zvirokwazvo, nomweya wangu nomuviri wanguvo.
\v 10 Nokuti hupenyu hwangu hwapera nokuchema, namakore angu nokugomera; Simba rangu rapera nokuda kwokutadza kwangu, uye mapfupa angu asakara.
\v 11 Ndava chinhu chinozvidzwa nemhaka yavadzivisi vangu vose, Zvirokwazvo, zvikuru kuna vandinogara navo, nechinotyisa kuvazikani vangu; Vakandiona kunze vakanditiza.
\v 12 Ndakanganikwa sowakafa asati achafungwa; Ndava somudziyo wakaputsika.
\v 13 Ndakanzwa vazhinji vachindipomera, Zvinotyisa kumativi ose; Pakurangana kwavo pamusoro pangu Vakafunga mano kuti vanditorere upenyu hwangu.
\v 14 Asi ndakavimba nemi Jehovha; Ndakati, "Ndimi Mwari wangu."
\v 15 Nguva dzangu dziri muruoko rwenyu; Ndirwirei paruoko rwavavengi vangu, nokuna vanonditambudza.
\v 16 Vhenekesai chiso chenyu pamusoro pomuranda wenyu; Ndiponesei nounyoro hwenyu.
\v 17 Ngandirege kunyadziswa, Jehovha; nokuti ndakadana kwamuri; Vakaipa ngavanyadziswe, ngavanyarare paSheori.
\v 18 Miromo inoreva nhema ngainyarare; Iyo inotaura namanyawi kuna vakarurama, Ichizvikudza nokuvazvidza. Haiwa, zvakanaka zvenyu zvamakachengetera vanokutyai zvakakura sei, Zvamakaitira vanovimba nemi, pamberi pavanakomana vavanhu!
\v 19 Muchavavanza pakavanda pamberi penyu, vabve pamano avanhu;
\v 20 Muchavachengeta pakavanda patende vabve panharo dzendimi.
\v 21 Jehovha ngaavongwe, Nokuti akandiratidza unyoro hwake hunoshamisa paguta rakasimba.
\v 22 Kana ndirini, ndakati pakukaruka kwangu, "Ndabviswa pamberi penyu;" Kunyange zvakadaro, makanzwa inzwi rokukumbira kwangu pakuchema kwangu kwamuri.
\v 23 Idai Jehovha, imi vatsvene vake mose; Jehovha anochengeta vakatendeka, Anotsiva zvikuru munhu anozvikudza.
\v 24 Ivai nesimba, uye moyo yenyu itsunge, Imi mose munorindira Jehovha.
